	(HAVE_TM_GMTOFF): New symbol.
	(AC_CHECK_FUNCS): Add __fpending, ftello, getloadavg, mblen,
	mbrlen, strsignal.
	(LOCALTIME_CACHE): Don't include stdlib.h, as config.h does this now.

